Definition v_rep_ok_def:
  v_rep_ok v ‚áî
    ‚àÄa ts.
      Branch a ts ‚àà subtrees v ‚áí
        case a of
          Constructor' s => LFINITE ts
        | _ => ts = LNIL
End

Theorem v_inhabited[local]:
  ‚àÉf. v_rep_ok f
Proof
  qexists_tac ‚ÄòBranch Error' LNIL‚Äô
  \\ simp [v_rep_ok_def, subtrees]
QED

